author: asankha
msg: Add support into JMS transport to wrap non-soap/xml text and binary messages into a SOAP envelope
Two new service level parameters named transport.jms.Operation and transport.jms.Wrapper are introduced

to specify the QNames of the operation to invoke on such messages (defaults to an operation named urn:mediate) and the QName of the element which will wrap the contents within the SOAP body (defaults to jmsMessage in the axis2 namespace)
